1. *Mlada* devojka je izuzetno inteligentna. (The young girl is extremely intelligent.)
2. *Mlade* životinje su obično mnogo bučnije od odraslih. (Young animals are usually much noisier than adults.)
3. *Mladu* decu treba učiti da budu disciplinovani. (Young children should be taught to be disciplined.)
4. *Mladim* ljudima je potreban savet starijih. (Young people need advice from the elderly.)
5. *Mladoj* generaciji treba dati priliku da se iskaže. (The young generation should be given a chance to express itself.)